		  <td valign="top" class="style1" colspan="2" height="412">
		  <p>
		    <span class="style4"><span class="style3"><strong>MELISENDE</strong>  seeks to publish original studies, both contemporary and historical, on religion and politics, society, culture and art history in the Middle East, Africa and Asia.<br />
		    <br />
		  This includes work on religious studies, religion and politics, history, the relationship between religion and society, culture, anthropology, the philosophy of religion, comparative religion and spirituality, theology, Muslim-Christian relations, and ecumenism.<br />
		  <br />
		  We are happy to advise and provide a service for those individuals and organizations seeking to self-publish or who are looking for contract publishing.<br />
		  <br />
		  We provide a full service from editing, through all stages of production to sales and marketing.<br />
		  <br />
		  Please contact us to discuss your requirements or for further information.<br />
		  <br />
		  For Middle East sales and related Middle East titles, please see our associates’ website: <a href="http://www.rimalbooks.com">www.rimalbooks.com</a> </span></span></p>
